# Project: monday.com AI Platform Landing Pages

React + TypeScript + Vite + Tailwind CSS 4 + Supabase. Deployed on Vercel.

## Tech Stack

- **React 18.3** with react-router-dom 7.x
- **Vite 6.3** with `@tailwindcss/vite` (no separate tailwind.config)
- **TypeScript** (strict), path alias `@/*` → `./src/*`
- **Animation**: `motion/react` (Framer Motion)
- **Backend**: Supabase (URL: `fymyrxqjmnekcmrpvtju.supabase.co`)
- **UI**: Radix primitives, some MUI 7 components
- **Shell**: Windows PowerShell — no `&&` chaining, no heredocs

## Key Routes

| Path | Component | Description |
|------|-----------|-------------|
| `/` | `HomePage` | Main landing |
| `/agents` | `AgentsLandingPage` | Agent-focused landing page (primary focus) |
| `/platform` | `PlatformLandingPage` | Platform showcase |
| `/admin` | `AdminApp` | Admin dashboard |
| `/p/:slug` | `DynamicPage` | Supabase-driven pages |

